data.description: This is a Beauty and a Great Value!  Remodeled throughout, this open concept home features 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms.  Great kitchen with granite countertops and island, opening up to the spacious living room and dining area with vaulted ceiling and fireplace.  Wonderful private master suite with two walk in,closets, sitting area and Master bathroom with double sinks and large shower.   Backyard is private and offers a shed for extra storage and a large 2 car attached garage.  New windows throughout.  Downstairs bedrooms will have new carpet installed.  Contact Shay Thornton today for your personal tour at 307-258-1470.  GotCasperHomes.com
